### Order Service API Test File

### Create order
POST http://localhost:8081/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-001",
      "productName": "Laptop",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 999.99
    },
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-002",
      "productName": "Mouse",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 29.99
    }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/orders/1

### Get order by order number
GET http://localhost:8081/api/orders/number/ORD-1234567890

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health
